


{"id":2135,"date":"2016-04-19T12:52:14","date_gmt":"2016-04-19T11:52:14","guid":{"rendered":"http:\/\/jasservis.cz\/?page_id=2135"},"modified":"2026-05-16T18:00:08","modified_gmt":"2026-05-16T17:00:08","slug":"kompletni-diagnostika-vaseho-vozu","status":"publish","type":"page","link":"http:\/\/jasservis.cz\/kompletni-diagnostika-vaseho-vozu\/","title":{"rendered":"Kompletn\u00ed diagnostika va\u0161eho vozu"},"content":{"rendered":"<div class=\"mp-row-fluid motopress-row mpce-dsbl-margin-left mpce-dsbl-margin-right\">\n<div class=\"motopress-clmn mp-span6  mpce-dsbl-margin-left mpce-dsbl-margin-right\">\n<div class=\"motopress-code-obj\">\n<div class=\"row product-detail\"><div class=\"span6 \">U dne\u0161n\u00edch voz\u016f u\u017e v\u0161echny z\u00e1vady pouh\u00fdm pohledem pod kapotu neodhal\u00edte a slo\u017eit\u00e1 elektronika p\u0159iprav\u00ed nep\u0159\u00edjemn\u00e9 p\u0159ekvapen\u00ed nejednomu \u0159idi\u010di. P\u0159i diagnostice va\u0161eho automobilu proto postupujeme d\u016fkladn\u011b a komplexn\u011b. Pokud se p\u0159i kontrole projev\u00ed z\u00e1vada, zajist\u00edme v\u00e1m opravu a p\u0159\u00edpadn\u011b i dal\u0161\u00ed pot\u0159ebn\u00e9 slu\u017eby.<\/p>\n<h2><strong>ZNA\u010cKOV\u00c1 P\u00c9\u010cE O V\u00c1\u0160 V\u016eZ<\/strong><\/h2>\n<p>Pro vozidla zna\u010dek\u00a0<strong>Volkswagen, Audi, \u0160koda,\u00a0Seat, VW - u\u017eitkov\u00e9 vozy<\/strong>\u00a0\u00a0pou\u017e\u00edv\u00e1me v\u00fdhradn\u011b origin\u00e1ln\u00ed p\u0159\u00edpravky a za\u0159\u00edzen\u00ed schv\u00e1len\u00e9 koncernem\u00a0<strong>Volkswagen\u00a0AG.<\/strong><\/p>\n<h2><strong>KONTROLA ELEKTRONICK\u00ddCH\u00a0 SYST\u00c9M\u016e<\/strong><\/h2>\n<p>V r\u00e1mci diagnostiky prob\u00edh\u00e1 kontrola v\u0161ech elektronick\u00fdch\u00a0\u00a0syst\u00e9m\u016f vozidla. K dispozici m\u00e1me origin\u00e1ln\u00ed diagnostiku pro vozidla\u00a0<strong>Volkswagen\u00a0AG - ODIS<\/strong>\u00a0,<b> <\/b>multizna\u010dkovou diagnostiku\u00a0<strong>VCDS<\/strong>,\u00a0<strong>Bosch a Atal.<\/strong><\/p>\n<h2><strong>SPECI\u00c1LN\u00cd DIAGNOSTICK\u00c9 FUNKCE<\/strong><\/h2>\n<p><strong>U vozidel skupiny VW AG prov\u00e1d\u00edme i diagnostick\u00e9 funkce podl\u00e9haj\u00edc\u00ed utajen\u00ed a ochran\u011b komponent\u016f ( GeKo ) .\u00a0 Mezi n\u011b pat\u0159\u00ed : k\u00f3dov\u00e1n\u00ed imobiliz\u00e9ru, navigace, p\u0159izp\u016fsoben\u00ed kl\u00ed\u010d\u016f od vozidla a pod. Tyto funkce prov\u00e1d\u00edme pouze p\u0159i p\u0159edlo\u017een\u00ed p\u0159\u00edslu\u0161n\u00fdch dokument\u016f ( VTP,OP majitele vozidla )<\/strong><\/p>\n<p>Kompletn\u00ed diagnostika vozu v\u00e1m zabere max. 30 minut. Pokud neodhal\u00edme \u017e\u00e1dn\u00e9 z\u00e1vady, do p\u016fl hodiny m\u016f\u017eete bez obav odjet.<br \/><\/div><\/div><!-- .row (end) -->\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<div class=\"motopress-clmn mp-span6  mpce-dsbl-margin-left mpce-dsbl-margin-right\">\n<div class=\"motopress-image-obj motopress-text-align-left\"><img src=\"http:\/\/jasservis.cz\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/05\/diagnostika-1.jpg\" title=\"diagnostika\" alt=\"diagnostika\" class=\"motopress-image-obj-basic mpce-dsbl-margin-left mpce-dsbl-margin-right mpce-dsbl-margin-top mpce-dsbl-margin-bottom\" \/><\/div>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<div class=\"mp-row-fluid motopress-row mpce-dsbl-margin-left mpce-dsbl-margin-right\">\n<div class=\"motopress-clmn mp-span12  mpce-dsbl-margin-left mpce-dsbl-margin-right\">\n<div class=\"content_box call-to-action-row \"> <div class=\"row \"> <div class=\"span12 \"><p>Diagnostickou kontrolu sv\u00e9ho vozu objedn\u00e1vejte na telefonn\u00edch \u010d\u00edslech <a href=\"tel:+420 608 313 437\">+420 605 399 448, +420 608 313 437<\/a><br \/>\n(Po-P\u00e1 od 9 do 18 hod.)<\/p><\/div> <\/div><!-- .row (end) --> <div class=\"clear\"><\/div><\/div><!-- .content_box (end) -->\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"U dne\u0161n\u00edch voz\u016f u\u017e v\u0161echny z\u00e1vady pouh\u00f